title: Household rent to income ratio in the United Kingdom ( UK ) 2018 - 2019 , by region
summary: This grouped bar chart shows SOME LABEL on the Y-axis for 14 different Regions for 2 groups Oct' 18, and Oct '19 that are presented on the X-axis.
Out of all 2 groups, Oct' 18 had the highest SOME LABEL in Region London and Oct' 18 had the lowest SOME LABEL in Region Yorkshire & Humber.
In Region London, Oct' 18 had the maximum SOME LABEL and it saw the lowest in Region Yorkshire & Humber out of all 14 Regions.
Region London and Yorkshire & Humber had the biggest gap of 340.0 between the highest and lowest SOME LABEL found for Oct' 18.
